public class CHS
extends java.lang.Object

This class describe a chromosomal homology segment(CHS), which contains a pair of GenoLocs .

sortLocs

public void sortLocs()
Sort Genoloc A and B. If A is 'larger' compared with B, they are interchanged with each other.

compareTo

public int compareTo(CHS other)
Descend from the Comparable interface and compare the CHS object with another one. If their GenoLocs are not located in the same chromosome, they are compared by theri name; otherwise by theri start point.

指定者：
接口 java.lang.Comparable<CHS> 中的 compareTo
参数：
other - another CHS object
返回：
the difference according to the comparison rule
